<use f='linux-5.3.1/drivers/base/component.c' l='744' c='component_add'/>
<use f='linux-5.3.1/drivers/base/component.c' l='744' u='a'/>
<doc f='linux-5.3.1/drivers/base/component.c' l='725'>/**
 * component_add - register a component
 * @dev: component device
 * @ops: component callbacks
 *
 * Register a new component for @dev. Functions in @ops will be called when the
 * aggregate driver is ready to bind the overall driver by calling
 * component_bind_all(). See also &amp;struct component_ops.
 *
 * The component needs to be unregistered at driver unload/disconnect by
 * calling component_del().
 *
 * See also component_add_typed() for a variant that allows multipled different
 * components on the same device.
 */</doc>
